e is plentiful in a Mediterranean diet.[3] For comparison: The spermidine content in human seminal plasma varies between approx. 15 and 50 mg/L (mean 31 mg/L)."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"難怪冬菇有種少少似精嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1de664086546a37ee9e4ba828052939442de5b9","tid":2497461,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b28588add578f7526e482535fe82f16771827a04","tid":2497461,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeab490089a3789b1d203007108a950b03e35f19","tid":2497461,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eacaf95dd1a537aa69ff69ec7ff9af15c0052e58","tid":2497461,"uid":154756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"fake news?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"樓主篇文似係ezone news，link 去Cell 呢個網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell-reports/fulltext/S2211-1247(21)00299-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell-reports%2Ffulltext%2FS2211-1247%2821%2900299-0&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=a179cc6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell-reports/fulltext/S2211-1247(21)00299-0</a><br />\n<br />\n而睇番亞精胺(Spermidine)，就咁wiki(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spermidine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSpermidine&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=afc5995a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spermidine</a>)，其實正常食物都有<br />\n<br />\nSources<br />\nGood dietary sources of spermidine are aged cheese, mushrooms, soy products, legumes, corn, and whole grains.[14] Spermidine is plentiful in a Mediterranean diet.[3] For comparison: The spermidine content in human seminal plasma varies between approx. 15 and 50 mg/L (mean 31 mg/L)."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"難怪冬菇有種少少似精嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces